          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-05-30 19:01:14" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>a stream or river which flows only during the rainy season (in Palestine this would be during the winter months) or when melting snow from the mountains provides running water for a relatively short period of time</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>brook</Gloss>
                <Gloss>winter stream</Gloss>
                <Gloss>rainy-season stream</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>The reference in {S:04301800100022} is probably to the narrow valley, not to the stream itself, as noted in {D:1.52}.</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
          <LEXReferences>
            <LEXReference>04301800100022</LEXReference>
          </LEXReferences>
